history.content:
I'm looking for a Reader for CS 194-031 "Technological and social networks: Theory and analysis".  Some knowledge of network analysis and experience with relevant software (such as networkx) is preferred. If interested send a description of your background in this area and an unofficial transcript to ejf27@berkeley.edu. You will also need to complete a department application here.

-Professor Eric Friedman
history.subject: CS 194-031 Seeking Fall Readers
